{#  Refactorer Specialist Template

  Code refactoring without behavior change. Extract method,
  rename, decouple, simplify, reduce duplication. Reads
  existing code, identifies improvement targets, and produces
  refactored versions with clear before/after rationale.
  Agentic: applies changes, runs tests to verify.
